<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-4591] XPath will lock File input in case of an exception during xpath evaluation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-4591</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We have a similar issue with XPath, as we had with XSLT and XQuery.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If the message is a java.io.File and an exception occurs during evaluation, then that file is locked on Windows platforms.&lt;br/&gt;
We need to close the FileInputStream to unlock the file, and allow Windows to access the file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
